.com/artists/disclosure">Disclosure</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-national">The National</a>预计将在其他舞台上名列前茅。其他乐队还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-streets">The Streets</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justice">Justice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bloc-party">Bloc Party</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/arlo-parks">Arlo Parks</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gossip">Gossip 等</a>。</p><p>网上的大部分讨论都集中在 SZA 身上，他之前从未在 Worthy Farm 演出过，因此将成为 Glasto 的榜首。</p><p>就在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sza-channel-her-inner-uma-thurman-in-bloody-new-video-for-kill-bill-3378444">这位 R&amp;B 歌手在 2024 年全英音乐奖上被评为年度国际艺术家</a>后不久，就宣布了这一消息。 SZA 广受好评的 2022 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sza-sos-album-review-3363471">《SOS》</a>中的热门单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-sza-channel-her-inner-uma-thurman-in-bloody-new-video-for-kill-bill-3378444">《Kill Bill》</a>也在颁奖典礼上获得了年度国际歌曲类别提名。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4fLcwiNTQ7/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"